  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Алис, Боб хоёр ѳвлийн үдэш галын хажууд сонирхолтой бодлогууд бодон сууж байв. Алисын ээлж ирэхэд Бобод&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span>&nbsp;тоог хэлж: \"Үүнийг цифрүүдийн байрыг сэлгэж&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">0</span>-ээр эхлээгүй хамгийн бага тоог үүсгэ\" гэв. \"Асуудалгүй\" гэж Боб хариугаа олоод Алист ѳгѳв.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Алис ямар ч тоо хэлж болох бѳгѳѳд Бобын хариуг зѳв эсэхийг мэдэхгүй байв. Тэвчээргүй Боб хариугаа үнэн эсэхийг хүлээж ядаж байгаа тул түүнд тусална уу.</span></p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Эхний мѳрѳнд&nbsp;<span style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">0</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">-ээр эхлээгүй бүхэл тоо</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.600000381469727px; font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">n</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-5-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-13\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 8.065em;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 6.117em; height: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-15\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">(&nbsp;</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-16\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">0</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-17\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-18\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.165em; margin: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-19\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-20\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.165em; margin: 0px; font-style: italic;\">n</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-21\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-22\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.165em; margin: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-23\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span style=\"vertical-align: 0px;\">10</span><sup>9&nbsp;</sup>)</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;Хоёрдахь мѳрѳнд Бобын гаргасан хариу болох&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">m</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;бүхэл тоо,&nbsp;</span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-7-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-31\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 8.444em;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 6.388em; height: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-33\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">(</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-34\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">0</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-35\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-36\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.165em; margin: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-37\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-38\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.165em; margin: 0px; font-style: italic;\">m</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-39\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-40\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.165em; margin: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-41\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span style=\"vertical-align: 0px;\">10</span><sup>9</sup>),</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;урдаа</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.600000381469727px; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">0</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">-тэй тоо ч байж болно.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Бобын хариу зѳв бол&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Andale Mono', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier; font-size: 14px; color: #880000; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">OK</code><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">, бусад үед&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Andale Mono', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier; font-size: 14px; color: #880000; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">WRONG_ANSWER</code><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;гэж хэвлэ.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 1:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3310<br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1033</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Output 1:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small; color: #000000; line-height: 1.25em;\">OK</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 2:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">666<br></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">0666</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <strong>Output 2:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 16.25px;\"><span style=\"color: #880000; font-family: Consolas, 'Lucida Console', 'Andale Mono', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">WRONG_ANSWER</span></span></span></p>",
  "bodyText": "Алис, Боб хоёр ѳвлийн үдэш галын хажууд сонирхолтой бодлогууд бодон сууж байв. Алисын ээлж ирэхэд Бобод n тоог хэлж: \"Үүнийг цифрүүдийн байрыг сэлгэж 0-ээр эхлээгүй хамгийн бага тоог үүсгэ\" гэв. \"Асуудалгүй\" гэж Боб хариугаа олоод Алист ѳгѳв.\nАлис ямар ч тоо хэлж болох бѳгѳѳд Бобын хариуг зѳв эсэхийг мэдэхгүй байв. Тэвчээргүй Боб хариугаа үнэн эсэхийг хүлээж ядаж байгаа тул түүнд тусална уу.\nInput\nЭхний мѳрѳнд 0-ээр эхлээгүй бүхэл тоо n, ( 0 ≤ n ≤ 109 ) Хоёрдахь мѳрѳнд Бобын гаргасан хариу болох m бүхэл тоо, (0 ≤ m ≤ 109), урдаа 0-тэй тоо ч байж болно.\nOutput\nБобын хариу зѳв бол OK, бусад үед WRONG_ANSWER гэж хэвлэ.\nExample\nInput 1:\n3310\n1033\n \nOutput 1:\nOK\nInput 2: \n6660666\n Output 2: \nWRONG_ANSWER",
